---
import HwsLabLayout from '../../layouts/HwsLabLayout.astro'
import HwsLabPanel from '../../components/HwsLabPanel.astro'
---

<HwsLabLayout
  title="Lab page pattern"
  description="A modular page pattern for visual explanation, complex systems work and applied experiments."
  eyebrow="Example Lab"
  themes={["labs", "visual explanation", "systems"]}
>
  <HwsLabPanel title="Opening signal" wide>
    <p>This pattern gives complex work more room without turning the page into a decorative landing page.</p>
  </HwsLabPanel>

  <HwsLabPanel title="Context">
    <p>Use this space to explain what the Lab is exploring and why it matters.</p>
  </HwsLabPanel>

  <HwsLabPanel title="System view" variant="diagram">
    <p>A diagram, map, comparison or visual model can sit here.</p>
  </HwsLabPanel>

  <HwsLabPanel title="What it shows" wide>
    <p>The Lab should close the loop by turning visual exploration into usable insight.</p>
  </HwsLabPanel>
</HwsLabLayout>
